### Get Course by ID ###

# GET to fetch course by id (ID: 1)
GET http://localhost:3333/courses/1 HTTP/1.1

###

# GET to fetch course by id (ID: 5)
GET http://localhost:3333/courses/5 HTTP/1.1

###

# GET to fetch course by id (ID: 10)
GET http://localhost:3333/courses/10 HTTP/1.1

### Error Cases ###

# GET course with non-existent ID
GET http://localhost:3333/courses/9999 HTTP/1.1

###

# GET course with invalid ID (should return 400)
GET http://localhost:3333/courses/invalid HTTP/1.1

###

# GET course with negative ID (should return 400)
GET http://localhost:3333/courses/-1 HTTP/1.1
